OL,3,CCumbria set to see job advisors in GP
OL,4,Csurgeries
OL,6,FJob advisers in GP surgeries will be
OL,7,Fcoming to Cumbria as part of efforts
OL,8,Fto get 300,000 sick or disabled people
OL,9,Finto work by 2030 as the Government
OL,10,Fpledges to give people "a hand up, not
OL,11,Fa handout".
OL,13,FToo many people with health conditions
OL,14,Fare being written off and out of the
OL,15,Fjobs market, Work and Pensions
OL,16,FSecretary Pat McFadden said, adding
OL,17,Fthat this is something which "fails
OL,18,Four economy".
