OL,3,CCumbria set to see job advisors in GP
OL,4,Csurgeries
OL,6,FFunding of more than #1 billion across
OL,7,FEngland and Wales over the next five
OL,8,Fyears is aimed at getting tens of
OL,9,Fthousands more people into work.
OL,11,FCurrently there are approximately 2.8
OL,12,Fmillion people out of work in the UK
OL,13,Fdue to long-term sickness ` a figure
OL,14,Froughly equivalent to the population
OL,15,Fof Greater Manchester.
OL,17,FBenefit claimants can be supported by
OL,18,Fwork coaches at job centres in various
OL,19,Fways, including being offered advice
OL,20,Fand referred for job opportunities.
