OL,3,CCumbria set to see job advisors in GP
OL,4,Csurgeries
OL,6,FBut the Government said specialist
OL,7,Femployment advisers, which it
OL,8,Fdescribed as being different to work
OL,9,Fcoaches, are now being embedded into
OL,10,Fhealthcare teams, including GP
OL,11,Fsurgeries and mental health services,
OL,12,Fto ensure job support is treated as
OL,13,Fpart of the all-round care on offer.
OL,15,FIt is understood people will get
OL,16,Fintensive, personalised help including
OL,17,Findividual coaching from employment
OL,18,Fspecialists who understand complex
OL,19,Fbarriers to work.
