OL,3,CCumbria set to see job advisors in GP
OL,4,Csurgeries
OL,6,FMr McFadden said: "Writing off people
OL,7,Fwith long-term health conditions or
OL,8,Fdisabilities fails them and fails our
OL,9,Feconomy.
OL,11,F"We are giving people a hand up, not a
OL,12,Fhandout, realising their potential and
OL,13,Fproviding them with the skills to
OL,14,Fsucceed as part of our Plan for Change.
OL,16,F"Thanks to local areas hitting the
OL,17,Fground running, it is already
OL,18,Fdelivering results ` proving that when
OL,19,Fwe invest in people and communities,
OL,20,Feveryone wins."
