OL,3,CCumbria set to see job advisors in GP
OL,4,Csurgeries
OL,6,FThe plans are part of the Connect to
OL,7,FWork scheme, which is voluntary and
OL,8,Fopen to those who are disabled, have a
OL,9,Fhealth condition, or face complex
OL,10,Fbarriers to work.
OL,12,FA #167.2 million expansion of the
OL,13,Fprogramme into areas including
OL,14,FCumbria, Oxfordshire, and West Sussex
OL,15,Fand Brighton is expected to see more
OL,16,Fthan 40,000 more sick or disabled
OL,17,Fpeople get support into work.
