OL,3,CCumbria set to see job advisors in GP
OL,4,Csurgeries
OL,6,FUnemployed people and those who are in
OL,7,Fwork but at risk of losing their jobs
OL,8,Fbecause of the barriers created by
OL,9,Ftheir health conditions can refer
OL,10,Fthemselves for support or be referred
OL,11,Fby healthcare professionals, councils,
OL,12,For community organisations.
OL,14,FDisability campaigners welcomed extra
OL,15,Fsupport for people but warned the new
OL,16,Fmeasures should not end up forcing
OL,17,Fpeople into work.
