OL,3,CCumbria set to see job advisors in GP
OL,4,Csurgeries
OL,6,FJames Taylor, executive director of
OL,7,Fstrategy at disability equality
OL,8,Fcharity Scope, said the government
OL,9,F"must make sure it's not pressuring
OL,10,Fpeople who are not well enough to
OL,11,Fwork", while Mark Gale, policy manager
OL,12,Fat Sense, said it is "vital these
OL,13,Fmeasures are designed and delivered
OL,14,Falongside disabled people to bring
OL,15,Fabout meaningful change, and aren't
OL,16,Fsimply used to force people into jobs
OL,17,Fthat aren't suitable for their needs
OL,18,For may even be detrimental to their
OL,19,Fhealth".
