OL,3,CCumbria set to see job advisors in GP
OL,4,Csurgeries
OL,6,FAs well as availability of employment
OL,7,Fadvisers, people in areas including
OL,8,FPortsmouth, the North East and East
OL,9,FSussex will have access to virtual
OL,10,Freality immersive classrooms to help
OL,11,Fwith interview practice, workshops to
OL,12,Fimprove confidence and communication
OL,13,Fskills, and community-based health
OL,14,Fprogrammes.
OL,16,FParents will also be helped with
OL,17,Faccess to affordable childcare to
OL,18,Fenable them to get back into the
OL,19,Fworkforce, the Department for Work and
OL,20,FPensions said.
