OL,6,FThe government has previously warned
OL,7,Fthat if the welfare system is not
OL,8,Freformed, the number of working-age
OL,9,Fpeople on disability benefits is set
OL,10,Fto more than double this decade to 4.3
OL,11,Fmillion, and spending on working-age
OL,12,Fdisability and incapacity benefits
OL,13,Fwill rise to #70 billion a year by the
OL,14,Fend of this Parliament in 2029/30.
